################################################################################

autocmd DocStart ^https://mail.google.com mode ignore

autocmd DocStart ^https://tweetdeck.twitter.com mode ignore

autocmd DocStart ^https://feedly.com/ mode ignore

autocmd DocStart ^https://gather.town/ mode ignore

autocmd DocStart ^https://app.slack.com/ mode ignore

autocmd DocStart ^https://www.notion.so/ mode ignore

autocmd DocStart ^https://ap-northeast-1.console.aws.amazon.com/cloudwatch/ highlightcloudwatchlogs
